<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id79f581a9-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1996—<ref href="/us/pl/104/332/s2/h/1">Pub. L. 104–332, § 2(h)(1)</ref>, made technical amendment to <ref href="/us/pl/101/646/s1207">Pub. L. 101–646, § 1207</ref>, which enacted this section.</p>
